All Implemented Interfaces:
BiN2NMap<K,V>, N2NMap<K,V>
public class BiHashN2NMap<K,V>
extends HashN2NMap<K,V>
implements BiN2NMap<K,V>

A bidirectional mapping from possibly multiple keys to possibly multiple values implemented using HashMaps.

Attention: The implementation is backed by the returned sets. Changing these returned sets will change the mapping and may result in inconsistent behaviour!
